gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 113, Bucks 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Bucks, 113-107 as they have now won four of their last six games and improved to 33-15. Jamal Murray (35 points, five assists) and Nikola Jokic (league leading 14th triple-double: 25 points, 16 rebounds, 12 assists) led the Nuggets in the win. Giannis Antetokounmpo (29 points, 12 rebounds, four assists) led the Bucks, as they moved to 32-15 on the year.
